value: Resident, lowland forest: Sierra Leone - N and W Gabon, across N DRC to W Uganda.

primary & secondary lowland rain forest, in ravines & along forest streams overhung by trees and bordered by rank undergrowth;also swampy and seasonally flooded forest, esp.w.mud, arrowroot & tree ferns
